headline: Key4Women Hosts Free Webinar - Empower Your Image: Mastering the Art of Strategic Dressing

headline: Truist Financial Corporation (TFC) Q2 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: Truist Financial (TFC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -1.09% and +0.10%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
